Package: fyi
Title: For Your Information - R Package Introspection for LLMs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Troy", "Hernandez", email = "troy@cornball.ai", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Complete R package introspection for LLM consumption. Surfaces
    internal (non-exported) functions, option names from source code, and full
    help documentation. A standalone alternative to btw that requires no
    dependencies. Output is structured markdown suitable for any LLM.
